## C# (System.Text.Json)

```csharp
using System.Text.Json.Serialization;

public class User
{
    [JsonPropertyName("first_name")]
    public string FirstName { get; set; }

    [JsonPropertyName("last_name")]
    public string LastName { get; set; }

    [JsonIgnore]
    public string Password { get; set; }
}
```

